      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in showroom condition and curated for the most discerning enthusiast. The exterior retains its original luster, free of imperfections, while the cabin remains in a pristine, factory-fresh state. Beyond its striking aesthetic, the vehicle has undergone a comprehensive technical evaluation to ensure mechanical superiority. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of investment-grade quality that delivers an uncompromising driving experience.",
