    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and perfectly maintained. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great home! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
