      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 in concours-ready condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through its six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, it boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a proactive Vanos system overhaul. The chassis remains taut with OEM+ suspension geometry, while the factory limited-slip differential ensures precise power delivery. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this vehicle displays zero paint imperfections and a showroom-fresh interior. A turn-key masterpiece for the discerning driver looking for a pure, analog experience.",
